And so we had two kids.

1853
02:22:07,000 --> 02:22:11,000
And I was trying to keep her from being addicted.

1854
02:22:11,000 --> 02:22:13,000
And you can never do that.

1855
02:22:13,000 --> 02:22:17,000
And so I struggled with that and became a gang counselor,

1856
