We went five different schools.

1864
02:22:40,000 --> 02:22:44,000
We started the first media literacy program in a high school here in Seattle.

1865
02:22:44,000 --> 02:22:47,000
We took a group of kids to the world,

1866
02:22:47,000 --> 02:22:51,000
